Basically, the Gore Magala is a big dragon covered in decaying, black scales that it sheds everywhere as an infection overtakes it. Its eyes are covered and when enraged horns completely enshroud it. The scales it spreads makes all of the wildlife hyper berserk, meaning it's priority target number 1 by everyone in order to avoid a full on bloodbath.

After seemingly killing it, it molts its decayed scales and emerges golden and pure with a new name calling it Shagaru Magala. It was then classified as one of the elder dragons, which are essentially a bunch of animals and things collected together in a big "I don't know how the fuck these assholes do their weird magic bullshit", since the others have biological tools and organs that help them spit fire or electricity, while these guys can create tornados out of thin air, levitate, or summon giant meteorites or lasers out of the sky. There's also the Chaotic Gore Magala, which is a Gore Magala that only got halfway through molting.
